## Basic

<div class="max-w-2xl">
	<ReasoningTrace content="The user wants a simple example. I'll provide one." />
</div>

## Expanded

<div class="max-w-2xl">
	<ReasoningTrace content={sampleReasoning} expanded={true} />
</div>

## In Context

Used inside a `Message` component via the `thinkContent` prop, the reasoning trace appears between the header and the message body.

